Package: bib2academic
Type: Package
Title: Convert BibTex to Markdown for the Hugo Academic Theme
Version: 0.1.0.99
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Peter Baumgartner <peter.baumgartner@icloud.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Lorenzo Busseti <lbusett@gmail.com> [ctb]"
  ))
Description: Convert records of a BibTeX file (.bib) to separate .md files
    for the publications folder of the Hugo Academic Theme. Store optionally
    also each record as a separate .bib file for the '/static/files/citations' 
    folder.
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Date: 2018-08-04
Contact: Peter Baumgartner <peter.baumgartner@icloud.com>
URL: https://github.com/petzi53/bib2academic
BugReports: http://github.com/petzi53/bib2academic/issues
License: CC BY-SA 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
